@node WASSOLLDAS "Was soll das ?"

    Always I was looking for a resistor, in my mind was a black whole about
    the colored code of the resistors ... :-?

    What means the blue ring ... ?

    Was there a red or orange ring at a 10 KOhm resistor ... ?

    Such have now a end ... there is a program ... :-))

            RESISTOR

    Some people (such, they don't build electronics by itself) will say:

    This program is nonsence ...  OK  ...  but  the  rest  will  be  (sure,
    hopeful?) enjoyed ...

    The program is a, not nearest perfect, useful tool.

    First I thought to make real colors in the  programs.  But  I've  seen:
    this will be a big expenditure of work for such a simple program.

    And also it would need a minimum of 16 color at the workbench.

    So I made this simple variant.

    Have fun !

